cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper discusses a new approach to reinforcement learning that primarily uses supervised learning techniques. Therefore, it is likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with training agents, which suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, since the approach involves neural networks, it could also be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
